1.1.1.1 Deck Mounted Consoles
    1. Conditions signal and read data from the machinery sensors and actuators.

1.1.1.1 Deck Mounted Consoles
    2. Sends digitized data to the operator consoles and receives common data from these same

1.1.1.1 Deck Mounted Consoles
    3. It converts digitized data from the operator consoles to discrete analog and digital control

1.1.1.1 Deck Mounted Consoles
    4. Runs the control algorithms for the equipment the VRTU is responsible for controlling.

